Move - Click, hold, and drag the desired axis to move object. {"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/a\/af\/MoveObject.jpg\/460px-MoveObject.jpg","bigUrl":"\/images\/thumb\/a\/af\/MoveObject.jpg\/726px-MoveObject.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":354,"bigWidth":"727","bigHeight":"560","licensing":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>License: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Fair_use\">Fair Use<\/a> (screenshot)<br>\n<\/p><\/div>"}


